What you need to know:

Amina said that they have come up with the slogan so as to inspire not only the athletes but all Kenyans to work towards the Tokyo Summer Games and the next 2024 Paris GamesAmina said that the website, https://teamkenya.or.ke/, will have stories on the happenings at Team Kenya training among other inspiring stories and photos from both active and former OlympiansAmina said she hopes the campaign will create a movement of young people who will be joined by the rest of Kenyans to make sure that the athletes feel the support of their country and compatriots